OL,3,CBadenoch won't block Tory coalition
OL,4,Cwith Reform UK in Birmingham
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch says Conservatives
OL,7,Fwouldn't block coalitions with Reform
OL,8,FUK in Birmingham.
OL,10,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,11,Findicated she would not prevent local
OL,12,FConservative councillors from forming
OL,13,Fcoalitions with Reform UK in
OL,14,FBirmingham, even as she ruled out any
OL,15,Fnational-level deal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
