OL,3,CBadenoch won't block Tory coalition
OL,4,Cwith Reform UK in Birmingham
OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "There
OL,7,Fwon't even be the need to discuss a
OL,8,Fdeal. We are standing to win control
OL,9,Fof Birmingham Council in May."
OL,11,FBadenoch was in Conservative-run
OL,12,FSolihull today, setting out plans to
OL,13,Ffix potholes, but the political
OL,14,Flandscape in nearby Birmingham is more
OL,15,Funcertain.
OL,17,FLocally, the party says it is fighting
OL,18,Fto win an overall majority, but recent
OL,19,Fhistory shows coalition politics can
OL,20,Fbe unavoidable.
OL,26,@nD@]OUqD@^O]
