OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775127607
OL,3,CBadenoch won't block Tory coalition
OL,4,Cwith Reform UK in Birmingham
OL,6,FConservative councillors were last in
OL,7,Fcharge of Birmingham Council between
OL,8,F2004 and 2012 in coalition with the
OL,9,FLiberal Democrats.
OL,11,FSince then, some believe remarks from
OL,12,FRobert Jenrick, in which he commented
OL,13,Fon the lack of white faces during a
OL,14,Fvisit to Birmingham, have damaged the
OL,15,Fparty's reputation in the city.
OL,17,FJenrick later doubled down on these
OL,18,Fcomments in March last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
